title: 2016 Piala Presiden (Malaysia)
text:
The 2015 Piala Presiden (referred to as the President's Cup) is the 32nd season of the Piala Presiden since its establishment in 1985. The league is currently the youth level (U21) football league in Malaysia. <a href="Kelantan%20FA">Kelantan U21</a> are the defending champions.
Rule changes.
The Piala Presiden is the amateur <a href="football%20%28soccer%29">football</a> competition in <a href="Malaysia">Malaysia</a> for under-21 players. Since its inception in 1985, the Piala Presiden has been the major tournament for under-21 and under-23 players. In 2009, the format of the competition was changed with only under-20 players eligible to be fielded for the tournament. In 2015 the format of the competition reverted to the original format with under-21 players..
